(102, 62, 'page_builder_0_content', '<h1>Metaverse, where Mythology meets blockchain</h1>\r\nMultiverse of Legends is a web3 project where you can immerse into the magical universe of mythology, create and trade in-game assets, earn while playing and explore world intangible heritage.'),
