(4470, 133, 'page_builder_2_content', '<h2>Join <em>unique platform</em>, where mythological heroes, legends of the past, rituals and artifacts are <em>embodied in the virtual world.</em></h2>\r\nWe build a platform that will give you an opportunities to have fun, explore, create, earn and contribute to society in truly magical virtual environment… and beyond.'),
