(7323, 153, 'page_builder_0_content', '<h1>Metaverse, <em>where Mythology</em> meets blockchain</h1>\r\nMultiverse of Legends is a web3 project where you can immerse into the magical universe of mythology, create and trade in-game assets, earn while playing and explore world intangible heritage.'),
