(9475, 164, 'page_builder_1_content', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Become a real <em>Legend!</em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"checkViewport fadeIn\">Magical Worlds of myths and legends have always been hidden from common people. Until now. The new Metaverse will give you an opportunity to reach the mythological lands, join Gods &amp; Heroes in their eternal war with Chaos and possibly become a Legend for the future generations!</p>'),
(9476, 164, '_page_builder_1_content', 'field_6329bbadd43c3'),
