(10419, 197, 'page_builder_1_content', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Become a real <em>Legend!</em></h2>\r\n<p class=\"checkViewport fadeIn\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Magical Worlds of myths and legends have always been hidden from common people. Until now. The new Metaverse will give you an opportunity to reach the mythological lands, join Gods &amp; Heroes in their eternal war with Chaos and possibly become a Legend for the future generations!</p>'),
(10420, 197, '_page_builder_1_content', 'field_6329bbadd43c3'),
